-- Japan Calls for Improved Maritime Communications With China, Kyodo Says
-- B y   K a n a   N i s h i z a w a
-- 2010-10-11T05:09:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/japan-calls-for-improved-maritime-communications-with-china-kyodo-says.html
Japanese Defense Minister Toshimi
Kitazawa, meeting with Chinese counterpart Liang Guanglie in the
Vietnamese capital of Hanoi today, called for prompt
establishment of maritime communications system between the two
nations to prevent incidents at sea, Kyodo News reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
